{"tid":825631,"cid":22,"subCid":0,"title":"LG電視HDR問題","createTime":"2018-09-17T16:36:05.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-17T23:40:07.000Z","uid":20664,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"8d854f9b14dd171d44ee4f43c5f3af0651f176bd","tid":825631,"uid":20664,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-17T16:36:05.000Z","msg":"是咁的，我有部LG 4K電視，型號係49UF6750<br />\n咁佢冇寫明支援HDR，但佢本說明書(睇最尾cap圖)有寫到只要開咗Ultra HD Deep Colour，<br />\n就可以支援輸入最高YCbCr 4:2:2 12bit，<br />\n咁我用電腦(GTX 1050 Ti)真係可以set輸出做YCbCr 4:2:2 12bpc，<br />\n但我部ps4 pro 剩係寫不支援HDR，唔理係HDCP 2.2定1.4都好都係開唔到HDR<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/09/18/000616_d99119ca42e35bfa7fbc7fba9ab1d88a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F09%2F18%2F000616_d99119ca42e35bfa7fbc7fba9ab1d88a.jpg&h=c7e356bc&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"cc31923cd825ea8bbb28a29e900fe2d4c6e4ad05","tid":825631,"uid":20664,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-17T16:53:43.000Z","msg":"利申：部電視唔洗錢所以先玩下<br />\n唔係太識<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncer.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1caab943453f2a1d5cca022aac53033872d652ec","tid":825631,"uid":79829,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-17T23:38:31.000Z","msg":"1999"},{"pid":"8c0a314a08b54e3c0a2198820002c3858805e0db","tid":825631,"uid":79829,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-17T23:40:07.000Z","msg":"HDR=High Dynamic Range"}]}